    "We then build an undirected network in which news outlets are represented as nodes and weighted edges indicate the level of similarity among them.",
    "We create one network for each country and topic considered to enable a fair comparison.",
    "The resulting networks are visualized in Fig 3.",
    "To highlight only the stronger connections, we discard edges with weights lower than the overall median of the edges of each network (see S1 and S2 Figs of SI for the results with the complete networks).",
    "We may observe variations in the network structure depending on the country and topic under consideration."
  ],
